vidson.edu">Laurie       Heyer</a></font></li>  <li><font size="5">SUPPORT: MAGIC Tool software is provided without warranty or guarantee of support. However, NSF funding allows us to  provide limited support via email to:<br>      <font color="#FF0000">magictool &quot;dot&quot; help &quot;at&quot; gmail &quot;dot&quot; com </font></font></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong><font size="5">D</font></strong><font size="5"><strong>ocumentation</strong></font></p><ul>  <li><font size="5"><a href="MAGIC%20Users%20Guide%20v1-6.pdf">User's Guide</a> (1.9 MB     PDF file)</font></li>  <li><a href="Spanish_MAGIC_UsersGuidev2.pdf"><font size="5">Herramienta MAGIC        Gu&iacute;a  del Usuario</font></a> <font size="5">(3.3 MB PDF)</font></li>  <li><font size="5"><a href="MAGIC_Instructor_Guide.pdf">Instructor's Guide </a>with additional math background for understanding data analysis (2.1     MB PDF file)</font></li>  <li><font color="#FF0000" size="5">NEW</font><font size="5"> <a href="tutorials/index.html">Flash Tutorials</a> -  animations illustrating how to use MAGIC Tool (More coming soon!) </font></li></ul><p>&nbsp;</p><p><font size="5"><strong><a href="Sample_Files.zip">Download small sample files</a> (1 grid and 4 grid) for practice</strong></font></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><font size="5"><strong>Download BIG tiff files for advanced practice</strong></font> </p><ul>  <li><font size="5">Whole yeast genome <font size="4">(Y01 Version from Stanford       - provided by Laura Hoopes </font><font size="5"><font size="4">and Jessica       Brown</font></font><font size="4">)</font></font>     <ul>      <li><font size="5"><a href="Big_Tiffs/Pomona/Pomona097_w685.tif">red Pomona097_w685.tif         </a>(12.4 MB .tif File)</font></li>      <li><font size="5"><a href="Big_Tiffs/Pomona/Pomona097_w595.tif">green Pomona097_w595.tif         </a>(12.4 MB .tif File)</font></li>      <li><font size="5"><a href="Big_Tiffs/Pomona/Pomona_Y01_merged.jpg">Jpeg        